```{r message=FALSE}
library(magrittr)
library(tidyverse)
```



```{r}
single_cell <-
  read_csv(
    "input/p38_single_cell.csv.gz",
    col_types = cols(
      P = col_integer(),
      R = col_integer(),
      C = col_integer(),
      Cmpd = col_character(),
      Conc = col_double(),
      Broad = col_double(),
      isrndm = col_logical(),
      KS5 = col_double(),
      KSP5 = col_double(),
      diff5 = col_double(),
      TLR5 = col_double()
    )
  )
```
